type="user">//forester/jms-00WG</fr:addr><fr:route>foreign-forester-jms-00WG.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="Dependency audit">Dependency audit</fr:title></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>In recent releases, Forester has become increasingly dependent on various system packages (including openssl) via transitive dependencies. This has caused a great deal of build breakage for both our developers and users, so we decided to remove all but the most critical dependencies to avoid losing control of things. Experimental tools that rely on more system dependencies that are likely to cause build breakage can be created, but only outside the main <fr:code>forester</fr:code> package.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
